==Comments==  
* Do we adopt names from a conventional viewpoint - as selling by licensor -, or as a sourcing agreement by licensee?  Issue comes in Sec 10- Licensee's personnel => Licensor.  
* Some of the names are long-ish because @hazardj is trying to make them consistent with a general classification system.  There is no strict need for this, but it will help as we use clauses from this as resources for all contracts.
* There is some instability in the naming.  Working on it.
* See [[NDA_Agt_Frame]] for the current trunk of the naming system.

