Click on "Render," just above.

This page can be used as a frame for all contract agreements.  It provides the basic elements of Prologue, Sections, Signature, and Attachments. You can see it instantiated with some more taxonomy at [[Demo:Model_Agt_Frame]]

<b>Note:</b> All agreements can be understood as four points -- Prologue, Sections, Signature and Attachments.  This page establishes that structure and provides a framework for Prologue and Signature.  It also provides some Section headings to suggest a classification.  As an example of party specifics, it includes a page for [[Relationship_Acme_Quake|Acme and Quake]].

See the discussion page for more explanation and introduction. 


Please give feedback on the nomenclature and semantic markers.  Each of the fields is also available à la carte, just prefix with "Model.", e.g., [[Model.Agt.Prologue]] 



